Continuous Monitoring --> why?

1. Health Check
2. Performance

Roles of a DevOps Engineer (Continuous Monitoring):
1. Perform POC on the monitoring tools
2. setup/install the monitoring tool
3. Creating Dashboards for metrics --> CPU, Memory Disk, Response time, status code, uptime
4. Alerting

Monitoring tools:
1. Prometheus & Grafana
2. ELK (Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana)
